SELECT * FROM ar_objects;

SELECT ua.user_id, ua.total_interactions, COUNT(*) AS session_count FROM user_analytics ua JOIN user_sessions us ON ua.user_id = us.user_id GROUP BY ua.user_id, ua.total_interactions HAVING COUNT(*) > 2 ORDER BY session_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM performance_analysis WHERE metric_value > 100 ORDER BY analysis_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT ua.user_id, ua.total_interactions, SUM(pa.metric_value) AS total_performance FROM user_analytics ua JOIN performance_analysis pa ON ua.user_id = pa.ar_object_id GROUP BY ua.user_id, ua.total_interactions ORDER BY total_performance DESC;
